Step, Description
Preparation, "Develop IR plans, train team, implement monitoring, run tabletop exercises."
Identification, "Detect and analyze incidents, confirm scope, type, and severity."
Containment, "Isolate affected systems, prevent lateral movement, preserve evidence."
Eradication, "Remove malware, malicious accounts, patch vulnerabilities."
Recovery, "Restore clean systems, monitor for reinfection, return to normal operations."
Lessons Learned, "Conduct post-mortem, update IR plans, share intelligence, improve defenses."
		
